4 * 4
area = 4 * 4

base = 4
height = 4
base * height

area = base * height

Assignment of variable with math:
-Right side evaluated first, then given to the left side

area = 4 * 4

base = 4
height = 4
area = base * height
height = 3

(area = 16, not 12 )

Volume of a box
length = 10
height =20
